title: Start
---
Convoy Tactician: Three bikes left the grid. Two echoes came back.
-> Ask for the route wafer
    Convoy Tactician: Burned at the edges, still warm enough to lie.
-> Ask who benefits
    Convoy Tactician: Anyone who can sell silence by the kilometer.
-> Take the job
    Convoy Tactician: Follow the dead air. Do not trust a clean ping.
